canonical:
  title: 次韻
  author: 李昌壽
  language: lzh
  text: 積翠西南不盡山夕陽啼鳥竹林間偶傾春酒二三酌一任東風料峭寒
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 次韻
  author: 李昌壽
  language: lzh
  text: 積翠西南不盡山。夕陽啼鳥竹林間。偶傾春酒二三酌。一任東風料峭寒。
korean:
  title: 차운
  author: 이창수
  language: kor
  text: |-
    서남에 쌓인 푸른 빛 한없는 메인데
    석양 대숲 사이에 새 우는 소리
    봄술 두세 잔을 우연히 기울일 제
    동녘 바람 차가움은 제대로 맡겨두리라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1460_010_0580&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 終南守 : '
    value: 저본에는 없다. 저본의 원목차에 근거하여 보충하였다.
english:
  title: Matching Rhymes
  author: Lee Chang-su
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Endless verdant mountains pile up toward the southwest.
    In the dusk, birdsong echoes through the bamboo grove.
    By chance I tilt back spring wine, cup after cup—
    Let the eastern wind's sharp chill have its way.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: This poem follows the rhyme scheme of another work, a common poetic practice in classical Chinese and Korean poetry where a poet would 'match rhymes' (차운/次韻) with an earlier composition.
